{
  "stem": "7458.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were cut to pieces in a matter of days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And soon after September 1st, the German army marched into Jasionowka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But to our amazement, they did not burn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They did not loot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They do not kill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were rather polite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they announced that the reason is that they had signed an agreement with Russia and that Jasionowka was going to be part of the Soviet sphere, so they cannot do anything.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They will be pulling out and the Russians will be pulling in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this is what happened a day or two later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Their Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Jewish people were very happy with that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my family had some concerns, because the Russians regarded anybody who owned a factory or a tannery as being a member of the-- of the capitalist establishment.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And many of them were deported to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In retrospect, it would have been a blessing had we been deported to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Minskis, who owned the largest tannery, were deported and most of them survived and ended up, eventually, in Israel after the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were not deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] once the Soviets came in, things changed for the better.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Officially, antisemitism was abolished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You could have somebody arrested for even a remark, an antisemitic remark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The government was against antisemitism As a practical matter, there was anti-Semitism among the Russians as well, but not sponsored by the government.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "As for myself, my school was changed form a Hebrew school to a Russian school-- school, called a [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Dziesiecletke, ?] which means a ten year school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Dziesiec ?] is ten.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Letke ?] is year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I suddenly realized that education is important.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
